 measures for protection, ETSU K/EL/00235/REP; Redfern, M.A., Barrett, J.I., Usta, O., A new microprocessor based islanding protection algorithm for dispersed storage and generation units (1995) IEEE Transactions on Power Delivery, 10 (3), pp. 1249-1254; Robitaille, M., Agbossou, K., Doumbia, M.L., Modeling of an islanding protection method for a hybrid renewable distributed generator (2005) Proc. of electrical and computer engineering, pp. 1477-1481. , Canada; 1-4 May; Redfern, M.A., Usta, O., Fielding, G., Protection against loss of utility grid supply for a dispersed storage and generation unit (1993) IEEE Transactions on Power Delivery, 8 (3), pp. 948-954; Bright, C.G., COROCOF: Comparison of rate of change of frequency protection: a solution to the detection of loss of mains (2001) developments in power system protection, conference, , publication no. 479, IEE©;; Econnect, (2005) Islanded operation of distribution networks, DG/CG/00026/00/00; Powell, L.J., An industrial view of utility cogeneration protection requirements (1988) IEEE Transactions on Industry Applications, 24 (1), pp. 75-81; Perera, N., Rajapakse, A.D., Agent-based protection scheme for distribution networks with distributed generators (2006) Proc. of IEEE power engineering society general meeting, , Montreal, Canada; 18-22 June; Celli, G., Pilo, F., Pisano, G., Allegranza, V., Cicoria, R., Iaria, A., Meshed vs. radial MV distribution network in presence of large amount of DG (2004) Proc. of IEEE PES power systems conference and exposition, 2 (10-13), pp. 709-714. , October; Brahma, S.M., Girgis, A.A., Development of adaptive protection scheme for distribution systems with high penetration of distributed generation (2004) IEEE Transactions on Power Delivery, 19 (1), pp. 56-63; Brahma, S.M., Girgis, A.A., Effect of distributed generation on protective device coordination in distribution system (2001) Proc. of large engineering systems conference on power engineering LESCOPE '01, pp. 115-119. , Ha